Welcome to Town Of Us Reworked %modversion%!

Town Of Us Reactivated but better! (hopefully)

This mod is a mish mash of code and ideas from different mods and forks, mainly from Town Of Us Reactivated and The Other Roles. Enjoy the chaos that comes out as a result!

If you want to know more try using the other info commands, visiting the %github% page or joining the %discord% server. Happy ejections!

Changelog-
- Improvement: The Random Spawns option has been expanded for additional options
- Improvement: Improved animations for when changing appearances
- Improvement: You can now cancel delays and effects by clicking the ability button again
- Critical Fix: Fixed not being able to vent properly in dlekS
- Bug Fix: Fixed the custom Polus Specimen and Mira Comms vents not being viable starting points for postmortal roles
- Bug Fix: Fixed the rare bug where using a Miner's vent might get you stuck in a walking animation against the wall
- Bug Fix: Hopefully fixed the role gen sorting issues
- Bug Fix: Fixed being able to carry bots over to online games from local
- Bug Fix: Fixed morphing not actually changing players' name and colorblind texts sometimes
- Bug Fix: Fixed modifiers, objectifiers and abilities sometimes appearing in the mod's Hide And Seek mode
- Visual Fix: Fixed Politician vote selection just skipping the animation
- Visual Fix: Fixed body color transitions appearing weird and sometimes turning the character black
- Potential Fix: Hopefully fixed the occasional stuttering

